  "description": "ForgeMT is a secure, scalable GitHub Actions runner platform for ephemeral workloads. Designed for multi-tenant environments, it automates isolated runner provisioning on Kubernetes or EC2, with built-in OIDC, IAM, cost optimization, and deep observability.",
